                  "level": 3,
                  "type": "heading"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Les yumkasaures peuvent cracher de la pectine de flammegrenade cachée dans leurs joues pour s'accrocher à des objets lourds ou à des symboles, avant de se hisser vers l'avant pour se déplacer. Ils peuvent même planer dans les airs et aller où ils veulent...",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/478710ccb5a7de10c5e61a50e5d479d2_8099333817210829253.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Les yumkasaures peuvent également utiliser la pectine de flamboigrenade pour attraper des légers dans leur bouche avant de viser pour les recracher.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/57cbaeba5b3f2cc1014a36ab7cae98f1_7739208691088580476.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(153, 255, 136)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Sceau de bobherbe",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Déplacement rapide",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/6daaada779e3024796643dbd6a1bce7c_8971735380285325577.gif"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:rgb(153, 255, 136)"
                      ],
                      "text": "Sceau de bobherbe spécial",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "text": "Après avoir été activé, ce sceau spécial peut créer une feuille de répit sur laquelle vous pouvez temporairement reposer vos pieds.",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "alignment": "center",
                      "type": "custom_image",
                      "url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/09/04/29705491/1624c9d7d8f66ff2b2430652fef19a05_8109681092275487185.png"
                    }
